Module it.polimi.ingsw.am11
Package it.polimi.ingsw.am11.view.client.miniModel

Class MiniGameModel

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.am11.view.client.miniModel.MiniGameModel
public class MiniGameModel extends Object
This is used to store the state of the game in the client, it is a stripped down verion of the GameLogic class, it is used to store only the necessary information to display the game on the client side, it has no logic.
